name: Get Count Item New Arrival
sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) as count
FROM `tabItem`
WHERE name IN (SELECT DISTINCT(variant_of) FROM `tabItem`) 
AND new_arrival = 1

name: Get Count Promo
sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) as count
FROM `tabItem`
WHERE name IN (SELECT DISTINCT(variant_of) FROM `tabItem`) 
AND flash_sale = "<flash_sale>"

description:
Ini perlu diubah ke AND item_group LIKE (<item_group>)
Sudah dipindah ke custom API
name: Get MIN MAX Item Filter
sql:
SELECT MAX(minimal_item_price) AS max, MIN(minimal_item_price) AS min FROM `tabItem` 
WHERE name IN (SELECT DISTINCT(variant_of) FROM `tabItem`) 
AND item_name LIKE "%<search>%" 
AND item_group LIKE "%<item_group>%"

name: Get Shop Website
sql:
SELECT name, item_code, item_name, item_group, brand, image,minimal_item_price AS item_price, LEAST(IFNULL(LOCATE("\"<customer>\"", _liked_by), 0), 1) AS is_liked FROM `tabItem` 
WHERE name IN (SELECT DISTINCT(variant_of) FROM `tabItem`) 
AND item_name LIKE "%<search>%" 
AND item_group IN (<item_group>)
AND brand IN (<brand>)
AND minimal_item_price >= <min_price>
AND minimal_item_price <= <max_price>
AND disabled = 0
ORDER BY <order_by>
LIMIT <limit> OFFSET <page>
variables:
search:
page:0
limit:20
item_group:"Akesoris","Baut","Body Parts","Knalpot","Radiator","RIM","Shockbreaker","Stang"
brand:"Others","ADELIN","RIZOMA","SEPP","ON DEMAND","BIONDI","EMC"
max_price:999999999999
min_price:0
order_by: modified DESC
customer:<frappe.session.user>

identifier: Get MIN MAX Filter Shop Website
name: Get MIN MAX Filter Shop Website
sql:
SELECT MAX(minimal_item_price) AS max, MIN(minimal_item_price) AS min FROM `tabItem` 
WHERE name IN (SELECT DISTINCT(variant_of) FROM `tabItem`) 
AND item_name LIKE "%<search>%" 
AND item_group IN (<item_group>)
AND brand IN (<brand>)

sql:

INNER JOIN `tabShopping Cart Item` ON `tabShopping Cart Item`.parent = `tabShopping Cart`.name 
WHERE `tabShopping Cart`.user = '<user>'

sql:
SELECT * , "<flash_sale>" as f_sale_template
FROM `tabItem`
WHERE name IN (SELECT DISTINCT(variant_of) FROM `tabItem`) 
AND item_name LIKE "%<search>%" 
AND item_group LIKE "%<item_group>%"
AND popular LIKE "<popular>" 
AND new_arrival LIKE "<new_arrival>"
AND (CASE
WHEN '<flash_sale>' = "" OR '<flash_sale>' is null OR '<flash_sale>' = "%%" OR '<flash_sale>' = "%" THEN 1
ELSE flash_sale LIKE "%<flash_sale>%"
END)
AND disabled_item = 0
AND minimal_item_price >= <min_price> AND maximal_item_price <= <max_price>
ORDER BY <order_by>
LIMIT <limit> OFFSET <page>
variables:
search:
page:0
limit:20
item_group:"Masker","Aksesoris Dapur"
popular:%
new_arrival:%
flash_sale:
min_price:0
max_price:999999999999999
order_by: item_price DESC

sql:
SELECT `tabShopping Cart Item`.*, `tabShopping Cart`.customer, `tabShopping Cart`.sales_person, "<price_list>" as 'price_list' FROM `tabShopping Cart` 
INNER JOIN `tabShopping Cart Item` ON `tabShopping Cart Item`.parent = `tabShopping Cart`.name 
WHERE `tabShopping Cart`.user = '<frappe.session.user>'
ORDER BY idx ASC

sql:
SELECT si.name, si.posting_date, si.customer, sii.*, IFNULL(r.rating,0) AS rating, IFNULL(r.feedback, "") AS feedback, IFNULL(r.creation, "") AS rating_date
    FROM `tabSales Invoice Item` sii
        LEFT JOIN `tabRating` r ON sii.parent = r.sales_invoice AND sii.item_code = r.item
        JOIN `tabSales Invoice` si ON si.name = sii.parent
WHERE sii.parent = '<sales_invoice>'

sql:
SELECT ti1.* , "<flash_sale>" as f_sale_template
FROM `tabItem` ti1 INNER JOIN `tabItem`ti2 ON ti1.name = ti2.variant_of
WHERE 
ti1.has_variants = 1
AND ti1.item_name LIKE "%<search>%" 
AND ti1.item_group LIKE "%<item_group>%"
AND ti1.popular LIKE "<popular>" 
AND ti1.new_arrival LIKE "<new_arrival>"
AND (CASE
WHEN '<flash_sale>' = "" OR '<flash_sale>' is null OR '<flash_sale>' = "%%" OR '<flash_sale>' = "%" THEN 1
ELSE ti2.flash_sale LIKE "%<flash_sale>%"
END)
GROUP BY ti1.item_name
LIMIT <limit> OFFSET <page>
variables:
search:
page:0
limit:20
item_group:
popular:%
new_arrival:%
flash_sale:Flash Sale Y

sql:
SELECT * , "<flash_sale>" as f_sale_template
FROM `tabItem`
WHERE name IN (SELECT DISTINCT(variant_of) FROM `tabItem`) 
AND item_name LIKE "%<search>%" 
AND item_group LIKE "%<item_group>%"
AND popular LIKE "<popular>" 
AND new_arrival LIKE "<new_arrival>"
AND (CASE
WHEN '<flash_sale>' = "" OR '<flash_sale>' is null OR '<flash_sale>' = "%%" OR '<flash_sale>' = "%" THEN 1
ELSE flash_sale LIKE "%<flash_sale>%"
END)
AND disabled_item = 0
AND minimal_item_price >= <min_price> AND maximal_item_price <= <max_price>
ORDER BY <order_by>
LIMIT <limit> OFFSET <page>

name: Get Item Category With Children
sql:
SELECT parent_item_group FROM `tabItem Group` JOIN
(SELECT DISTINCT(item_group) as item_group FROM `tabItem` WHERE item_group != "") tab ON (`tabItem Group`.name=tab.item_group )
GROUP BY parent_item_group

name: Get Item Category Child
sql:
SELECT name FROM `tabItem Group` JOIN
(SELECT DISTINCT(item_group) as item_group FROM `tabItem` WHERE item_group != "") tab ON (`tabItem Group`.name=tab.item_group AND `tabItem Group`.parent_item_group='<parent_item_group>')
